SHE THINKS THERE ARE
TWo SETS oF RULES:
HILLARY THINKS
SHES ABOVE
THE LAW!
ONE FOR THE
CLINTONS... AND

REST OF US!

RECOMMENDED
FOR HILLARY
BUT AT LEAST
SHE'S NOT
DONALD
TRUMP!
I TRUST HER

AS I CAN
THROW HER!

I'M WITH
ER
